76561198018652245,Recommended,257350,34769595,Posted: 5 September,all,Quenton,"One of the best games of all time. Games have tried to recapture the wonderfulness of this game with spiritual successors like Pillars of Eternity, Divinity: Original Sin (to an extent), and Tyranny, but honestly, you can't beat this game. This says I have 37 hours logged, but I've got probably 3 times that offline as well.Captivating story, unforgettable characters (Minsc? Irenicus? I mean come on!), and just enjoyable combat. Tactical and fun, where a battle can kick your butt until you change tactics, and suddenly you've unlocked the key. An instant classic that will always (in my opinion) stand the test of time."
